---
import AboutHeroImage from "../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg";
import Layout from "../layouts/BlogPost.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About Me"
  description="I am a frontend developer with a passion for fullstack backend, system design, and competitive sports."
  pubDate={new Date("April 10 2026")}
  heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
  <h1>Hello there! 👋</h1>

  <p>
    Welcome to my personal corner of the internet. I am a junior <strong
      >Frontend Developer</strong
    > with a strong drive to transition into a versatile <strong
      >Fullstack Engineer</strong
    >. My journey in software development is fueled by curiosity, a love for
    puzzle-solving, and a relentless desire to understand how things work under
    the hood.
  </p>

  <h2>My Technical Interests 💻</h2>
  <p>
    Beyond building beautiful user interfaces, I spend a lot of my time diving
    deep into the core mechanics of software engineering. My main areas of focus
    include:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Data Structures & Algorithms (DSA):</strong> I love the challenge of
      solving complex algorithmic problems efficiently and optimizing application
      logic.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>System Design:</strong> Architecting scalable, robust, and highly available
      systems from scratch is something that truly fascinates me.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Backend Engineering:</strong> I am actively expanding my skillset in
      server-side logic, databases, performance tuning, and API design to confidently
      build end-to-end applications.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Outside of Code 🏃‍♂️</h2>
  <p>
    When I'm not staring at a screen or debugging an obscure bug, you can
    usually find me <strong>playing sports</strong>. Physical activity is my
    favorite way of resetting my mind, maintaining discipline, and bringing a
    renewed focus back to my technical challenges. I strongly believe that a
    healthy body brings forth a sharp mind!
  </p>

  <p>
    This blog is a digital garden where I document my learning journey, share
    insights on frontend & backend development, and connect with like-minded
    developers. Feel free to explore my posts, and let's learn and grow
    together!
  </p>
</Layout>
